sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.CATEGORY LIKE "mde" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD = ( SELECT MIN( PROGRAM_COURSEalias1.WORKLOAD ) FROM PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias1 WHERE PROGRAM_COURSEalias1.CATEGORY LIKE "mde" ) ;

SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 ON PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID WHERE PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.CATEGORY LIKE "mde" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD = ( SELECT MIN( PROGRAM_COURSEalias1.WORKLOAD ) FROM PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias1 WHERE PROGRAM_COURSEalias1.CATEGORY LIKE "mde" ) ;
